articles.title: Mob faked attack on Australian synagogue: Police - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Police say organised crime gang fabricated a plan to bomb the Jewish site to divert law enforcement resources.
articles.content:
An organised crime network fabricated a plot to attack a synagogue in Australia to divert law enforcement resources, according to police.
